TY  - JOUR
T1  - Unpacking the Future: A Nudge Toward Wider Subjective Confidence Intervals
AU  - Jain, Kriti
AU  - Mukherjee, Kanchan
AU  - Bearden, J. Neil
AU  - Gaba, Anil
Y1  - 2013/04/04
PY  - 2013
